From the problem statement sources:

Email attachments → PDF, DOCX, XLSX, images
Maximo exports → CSV, XML
SharePoint → DOCX, XLSX, PPTX, PDF
WhatsApp → PDF, JPG, PNG
Hard copy scans → JPG, PNG, TIFF, PDF
Ad-hoc cloud links → anything above

So your complete file type list is:
Documents → PDF, DOCX, PPTX
Spreadsheets → XLSX, CSV, XML
Images → JPG, PNG, TIFF
Text → TXT
